If you use or extend ASaiM framework in your published work, please cite the following publications:

- Releases
  - v1.0.0: Bérénice Batut et al. (2016). v1.0.0 release of ASaiM framework,
    an open-source Galaxy-based opinionated framework dedicated to microbiota
    sequence analyses. Zenodo. [10.5281/zenodo.56282](https://zenodo.org/record/56282)

